  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Across the world, invitations were delivered. Under the watchful eye of the great master Dali Llama, the worlds greatest martial artists would return to a place they knew well.. Brutal Island. Each will use their own unique mental and physical martial arts style and training in a tournament to prove the worlds one true champion.",
